title: MP Dan Norris arrested on suspicion of rape, sexual assault and upskirting
summary_full: Labour suspended Norris, 66, last year after his original arrest on suspicion of child sexual abuse offencesDan Norris, a former Labour minister and now an independent MP, has been rearrested on suspicion of rape, sexual assault, voyeurism and upskirting, it is understood.Labour suspended Norris, 66, who defeated Jacob Rees-Mogg at the last election, last year after his original arrest.
